{"tid":33032,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黃翠如30秒喜怒哀樂　網民睇到心寒","createTime":"2016-12-10T14:22:58.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T14:28:49.000Z","uid":12342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"edf4f620204fc04a38f846a0326f091819c21b5c","tid":33032,"uid":12342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:22:58.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=a438569d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】尋日無綫劇《幕後玩家》大結局，黃翠如飾演的顧成雙為了復仇，毒害黃宗澤（Bosco）飾演的秦昇海致死，翠如喺醫院送Bosco最後一程時，30秒內喜怒哀樂的超班演技，獲網絡紅人杜如科大讚「真心好戲」。而網民都大讚翠如今次演技大躍進，網民都話翠如演個場戲，個樣又奸又陰險，睇到心寒之餘，直程隔住個MON都覺得佢有啲變態！ <br />\n<br />\n一向飾演「傻大姐」角色的翠如，今次挑戰呢個「魔鬼」角色，佢曾在東網的專訪中講過拍攝半年時間，心中非常難受，情緒好難過，對佢嚟講呢個角色係個大突破。今次結局反應咁好，相信翠如都會覺得努力冇白費。 <br />\n<br />\n而結局播完無耐，翠如即更新自己fb，再次解構成雙的內心世界，她留言：「她打從心底裏從來不覺得自己是一個壞人，她有自己的理由：生存的理由，致勝的理由，愛與恨的理由。在她的世界，從來只有她自己，她不需要別人的理解，認同和分享。有人覺得她是一個悲劇，有人覺得她非常可惡，但對於她來說，這就是她真實的人生。 <br />\n選擇，決定了命運。 <br />\n命運，決定了選擇。」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161210/mobile/bkn-20161210104123370-1210_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161210%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20161210104123370-1210_00862_001.html&d=lYTXLzsLZtpcSBTv5cf0w3vMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=d164466e\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20161210/mobile/bkn-20161210104123370-1210_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"03ca8f69fdf8b6e69a1995fc0fd27ae4c0ed635b","tid":33032,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22fd042a2b70f31b8a38fa5696254cdcdce59e88","tid":33032,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:27:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班網民食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"dbea52e32f53aff90e27ef388a74153cea46e68d","tid":33032,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T14:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>渣ga<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n班網民食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成班冇睇過人做戲"}]}